                    Next Level Vue
                    Course Notes


1 - Next-Level Vue Orientation
Intro to the course there are some prerequisites for taking the course
  - Vue CLI
  - Vue Router
  - Single File Components
  - API calls with Axios
  - Vuex
The course is a continuation of other courses
  - There is a sample app to be built
  - There is starting point code to the course to be downloaded
  - It is highly recommended that students follow along coding

